javax.microedition.lcdui.Choice, javax.microedition.lcdui.CommandListener
public class FileHandlerViewController
extends javax.microedition.lcdui.List
implements javax.microedition.lcdui.CommandListener

FileHandlerViewController is the main controller class to direct all operations. All data are printed in TextBox controll where user can make selection in order to target operations to spefific file / folder.
